§7§oThis gate has two inputs and four outputs.

The sides with torches are just outputs, while the sides with just redstone are both inputs and outputs.

When one input receives a pulse, both itself and its corresponding output will tun on indefinitely.

When the other input receives a pulse, the same will happen on the other side.

You can use buffer gates on the inputs to turn them into just inputs.
